#. Tag: para
#: man-checkXML6.1.docbook:34
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<command>checkXML</command> is a tool to check for syntax errors in &kde; "
#| "DocBook &XML; files. It can also be used for other DocBook based &XML; "
#| "files, but you should use the less specific xmllint(1) tool if you are "
#| "not writing or otherwise working on &kde; documentation."
msgid ""
"<command>checkXML6</command> is a tool to check for syntax errors in &kde; "
"DocBook &XML; files. It can also be used for other DocBook based &XML; "
"files, but you should use the less specific xmllint(1) tool if you are not "
"writing or otherwise working on &kde; documentation."
msgstr ""
"<command>checkXML</command> é unha ferramenta para procurar erros de sintaxe "
"en ficheiros &XML; DocBook de &kde;. Tamén pode ser empregada para outros "
"ficheiros &XML; baseados en DocBook, pero debería empregar a ferramenta "
"xmllint(1), que é menos específica, se non está a traballar na documentación "
"de &kde;."

